tagline.en: DappPub, Unleashing the Power of DApps

introduce.en: The DappPub node is a product & technology driven DApp development community node. DappPub adheres to the concept of high standard, high quality and high efficiency and it is rooted in the construction of blockchain DApp eco-related protocols and solutions, hoping to release the unlimited possibilities of DApp with products and technologies.
introduce.zh: DappPub节点是一个产品和技术驱动的Dapp开发社区节点。DappPub秉承高标准、高质量、高效率的理念，扎根于区块链DApp生态相关协议及解决方案的构建，希望用产品和技术来释放Dapp的无限可能。
